Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.38,0:00:03.72,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no shape to flowing water.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:05.32,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no figure to flowing winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:07.19,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No matter what the case, the deductions are free.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.79,0:00:09.12,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The melody lingering in her heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:10.66,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Brought upon a strange investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.12,0:00:12.56,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seeing through the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:14.26,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The appearance of a child but the brains of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:16.33,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name is: Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:45.58,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I, who stumbled onto a case and was wounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:48.19,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Managed to recover thanks to Ran donating her blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:52.19,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran knew about my true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:56.76,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So, with the antidote Haibara made,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.30,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I returned to Shin'ichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:01.03,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And with Haibara disguised as Conan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:03.40,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran's suspicions had disappeared, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Please, let it subside again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:16.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She's... she's waiting for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:21.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I... can't return to Conan yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:30.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ha-Haibara... you... why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:34.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}24 minutes over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:36.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I guess this is within the permitted range.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:43.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll return this to you, Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:51.92,Title,Sign,0,0,0,,The Poignant Music Box\N(Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Poignant Music Box. Part 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:55.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:02:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apotoxin 4869's antidote.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still have it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:02.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't say never, but I can't give it to a deducting\Nmaniac who can't hold himself back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll try to stop myself from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:18.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, that was only a prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't use an underdeveloped medicine for extended periods.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time, there is a real possibility that you may die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess with only Paikaru's ingredients,\Na full antidote can't be made.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, at least not without the drug's data.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:38.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, just be thankful that your identity wasn't revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:40.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I knew something like this would happen,\NI would've told Ran what I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, are you sure you're not going to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Haido Avenue's indoor pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are really cool waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:01.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I still have a small cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something good must've happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:16.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They served curry at school today, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's not like you, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were pretty excited about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.74,Dialogue Top,Sign,0,0,0,,Mouri Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:31.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I guess this means I have to restart from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah man, it's already summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:37.22,Signs,Note,0,0,0,,Note: Spring symbolizes a period of joy and relief from one's troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:37.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It doesn't look like spring will come anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:42.89,Dialogue Top,Note,0,0,0,,Translation Note: "Haru yo Koi" means "Come Dear Spring."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:42.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This song is... "Haru yo Koi?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:53.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you have a son as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's just a little freeloader that we're looking after.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with this music box?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some areas seem to have notes missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:09.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How old are you young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm around 7, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's only in first grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he always notices little things,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That become the hints to solving cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:21.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? A little detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:25.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, should we tell Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:30.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he'll find something that would lead us\Nto the person Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person she's looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:34.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:38.45,Dialogue Top,Note,0,0,0,,Bell buddies are friends that contact each other via pagers,\Nkind of like instant messenger programs now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:37.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bell buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person you're looking for is a bell buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:51.40,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Yuuki Haruna (21)\NFine Arts Major University Student
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:47.93,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I met him 3 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:52.40,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,When I became a fine arts student at the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt lonely because I couldn't make any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I just randomly entered a number\Non my pocket bell and sent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:00.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My name is Haruna,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:03.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to be my friend?" I wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then to my surprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:11.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got a response saying "My first love\Nwas also Haruna. Nice to meet you."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since, we've been bell buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was like a kind uncle who would listen to your every concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you sent "I wish to see you," in your\Npocket bell, then wouldn't he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have his pocket bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was last Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was getting harder and harder to pay\Ntuition while I was attending school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought about seeing him before I quit school and went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:56.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided to arrange a meeting with Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nin front of Shibuya station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no matter how long I waited, I didn't see anyone like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was about to give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I looked inside, this music box\Nwas in it along with his pocket bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did you know that was his pocket bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:22.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a message on that pocket bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"This is a very valuable music box."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:30.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Use it to pay for your schooling and don't\Ngive up on your dreams, Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't accept such valuable merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought maybe if I got the music box examined,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:41.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I might be able to find its owner and return it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I took it to an antique shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the person at the store only said\Nit was a broken, old, music box.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, weird messages have been sent to my pocket bell lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:07:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weird messages?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I have something to ask you."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Come to the location I tell you now, alone."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:11.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was different from the messages\NI received from Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got scared, so I didn't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:17.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, other messages were sent later that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It said "Cat Burglar!" more than 10 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:23.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over 10 times?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:26.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Cat Burglar?" Do you have any ideas as to why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I want to ask what the person's intentions\Nare, but I have no way to reach them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it might have something to\Ndo with Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, so I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that message is still coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it continued for some time, but it has stopped now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that means our only lead is this music box.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what we can get from a music\Nbox that is missing a few notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:55.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:09:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at the broken pins on the drum of the music box.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like they were old and broke off on their own,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:07.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But rather they were forcefully removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:08.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's some sort of message!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the music is "Come, Dear Spring," and the missing\Nnotes are near the end, "Ra, Do, and Ra."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Radora?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a monster you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know the lyrics to the missing notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lyrics are "onnmo e-he detai to matte iru," so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:32.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The missing ones are "Mo "De" and "Ru".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mo De Ru... Model!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:38.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who had that was a model!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:42.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, now that we know that, we can\Nsearch the model companies for...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:46.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be faster if we just go meet the person?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:50.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot, we can't do that, so we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s pocket bell number, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:56.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is tell officer Takagi the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:10:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then ask him to ask the pocket bell company,\Nand you'll at least find out his address.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:08.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found out the address and the phone number!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You might have more potential than Shin'ichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it was because of Officer Takagi that we got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was just a misuse of authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, are you sure\Nthey said we can go to their house?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, even though the one who answered\Nthe phone wasn't Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that everyone in his family\Nknew that he was into pocket bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I told them that I wish to return\Nhis pocket bell and music box,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They replied, "Please come!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be exciting to find out who Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'm Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:55.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:11:00.80,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Ogata Kazuko (50)\NFemale Head of the Ogata Family
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:00.90,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You weren't coming alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhh, we're just tagging along... I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we can talk about that later, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:07.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:10.85,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The rumored Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.95,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Ogata Shirou (22)\NSecond Son of the Ogata Family
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's have her rest in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was, after all, the pillar of Grandpa's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess we should put up some incense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:26.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Incense...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:32.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, he died at the end of last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:37.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:41.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By any chance, was Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} a model?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:50.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about this music box you say you received from my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:57.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard it was a very valuable music\Nbox, so I would like to return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:11:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh...? This music...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come, Dear Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:12.38,Signs,Note,0,0,0,,Note: The Japanese koto is a large string instrument, about six feet long. It is traditionally played on the floor. And it originated in China but, came to Japan in the 7th-8th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the music that Mother always played on Koto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:10.67,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Ogata Tsuneo (53)\NKazuko's Husband
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would Mother be the woman in that picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the woman next to Father is my mother,\NHaruna, who died 3 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:20.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haruna!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:22.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandpa probably thought of you as Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was very happy, saying: "Haruna came back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, excuse my rudeness,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To have a pocket bell at that age, he really is a unique individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, ever since Mother died, Father began\Nto take walks late into the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we gave him one in case of emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:13:00.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, was there anything inside the music box?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know... like... maybe a...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stamp, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:09.73,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,A stamp from a group of four, worth about 200 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:09.80,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Ogata Minoru (28)\NFirst Son of the Ogata Family
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason you came all the way to this house,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was because the old man told you where\Nit is and you came to find it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:20.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:24.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll reveal your true intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, get very comfortable, Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, please don't take it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His company isn't doing very well, so he's in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you came all this way, please stay for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.97,0:13:45.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We would like to hear more about you and Father's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:50.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is this about a 200 million yen stamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:55.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And what do the missing notes in that music box mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:58.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What in the world...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Question after question after question during dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poor Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To make it worse, it started to rain and it isn't letting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, other than this family's second born,\NShirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, everyone else is a bit weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at the back of Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s memoir stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The day he died was December 6th.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing strange about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said she received the music box last Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means if we believe what Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} says,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the one who gave Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} the music box\Nwas someone other than Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's forget about the bad things and get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An old man with a cane just went left down that hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no one here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I saw it go left!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only room to the left is ours...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:47.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my daughter says she saw a weird shadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was just their imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:16:01.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, the guest that slept\Nover last time said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They thought someone went by their pillows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something like this happened before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:13.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there should only be us in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:15.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Nii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't he taking a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey hey, now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:23.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sounded like a wire on an instrument was cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's the room with Mother's koto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi... Minoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:44.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Minoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:49.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minoru... hey Minoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:51.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Nii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:02.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This message...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:10.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:16.81,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then could that shadow of an old man,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this message be from the deceased Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once a person dies, he can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:32.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you have time to say stupid things, go call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:35.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-This might be a murder...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:36.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:40.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't consider me dead yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:41.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:43.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened, Nii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got hit on the head with something hard all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:50.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By something hard, you mean that koto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the koto that Grandma treasured!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:17:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't... Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.19,0:18:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you who hit me, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:03.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because when the loud sound came,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.66,0:18:09.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone was together in Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}'s room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then who the heck...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:18.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who? Didn't you see the culprit's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:18.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, your wound is on your forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:25.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means that you were hit from the front, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was too dark to see any faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that means when you were hit, this room was dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, by the time I noticed anything strange, it was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't that strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:41.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so strange about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what were you doing alone in a dark room?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:50.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:02.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:07.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} probably felt a presence in this room and came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, when he was about to turn the light\Non, someone hit him with the koto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Minoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what about the message sent\Nto Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s pocket bell, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was probably Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:33.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} probably had an appointment with a friend tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she had completely forgotten about it and came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meaning, that message was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From her friend who wanted to say "I've\Nbeen waiting for you for a while."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong, Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I don't remember making a promise like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, a lot has happened today, so I suppose anyone would forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:59.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what about the shadow of the old man I saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:05.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was the person who attacked my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But for an elderly man with a cane to hit a person\Nwith that heavy koto and knock him out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly, even if that elderly man existed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is probably impossible for him to knock out Minoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:23.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran says that elderly man disappeared just down the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if he wanted to run into the room\Nin the back, Conan and I were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:29.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:32.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That elderly man was most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like the old saying, "The true identity\Nof a ghost is just a dead tree."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, I really did...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You thought you saw a ghost because\Nyou're always so afraid of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:50.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:53.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either way, Madam, please call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like someone other than us was in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:07.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Was someone hiding here like Uncle said?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:10.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If so, what is that person's objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:15.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}From the looks of things, it doesn't look\Nlike it's been searched through.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:19.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That means it was a crime committed\Nspecifically against Minoru{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:23.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But this isn't Minoru{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:28.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I have a good idea why Minoru{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} was in this dark room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:34.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But how and when did the culprit know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.11,0:21:37.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And the koto that was used as the weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:42.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Was there a reason behind the culprit\Nusing the koto as the weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:47.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it, there's so many things I still don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:50.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The shadow of an old man that Ran saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:55.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Was that really just Ran's imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.26,0:21:57.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And finally, one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:22:00.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That music box with the missing notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:05.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That music box must be hiding an important secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:10.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The location of the hidden object that the\Npeople of this house are looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:16.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The 200 million yen stamp that Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} had!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.24,0:23:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this sharp for?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.57,0:23:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's the key signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.61,0:23:52.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Key signature?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.28,0:23:57.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I received the music box last Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:24:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be, father died on December 6th last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.49,0:24:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.39,0:24:06.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it the doings of a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.86,0:24:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Co-Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.53,0:24:15.57,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,The Poignant Music Box\N(Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.46,0:24:11.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.93,0:24:14.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Poignant Music Box (Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.37,0:24:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.74,0:24:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Electric Fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.87,0:24:22.44,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time is my dreaded music tangle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.51,0:24:24.44,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Secret of my heart!
